                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77 Chinese Eastern/101: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-07-24T15:00:00+08:00"
                            >July 24, 1929—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 24—1:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>622. My 612, July 24 [<hi rend="italic">23</hi>], 4 p.m. Following from Military
                    Attaché now at Mukden: <pb facs="0381" n="237" xml:id="pg_237"/>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“July 23, 9 a.m. Absence of military preparations together with official
                            assertions of determined passive attitude here convince me local
                            government has no intention of accepting possible Russian challenge.
                            Responsible Japanese believe that Russia contemplates nothing more than
                            demonstration on frontier. Officials declare that all negotiations now
                            in hands of Nanking. Tendency to admit that final steps in Harbin were
                            precipitate and to place responsibility for unauthorized action on
                            President Lu Jung-huan.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
